Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs45}抄網 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經兼職三個星期了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.90,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也更加享受這份工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 更讓我感到享受的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作後的船上釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小島 蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那個 是魚群
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.21,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}魚群是最讓垂釣者熱血沸騰的詞語了。 這指的是被捕食的小魚正在被捕食它們的大魚所追趕，追至水面撲騰的狀態。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚群？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是水面上聚集的小魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 在它們下面有著想吃掉它們的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能是金槍魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是把金槍魚專用的釣竿帶來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚也能釣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過沒那麼簡單就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.83,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)\b1\pos(1005,603)}戰慄的splash
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35\c&H9E4B2F&\3c&HFFFFFF&}splash指的是濺起的水花，使用popper這種擬餌來濺起水花就叫做splash。\Npopper中文也被叫做波扒，是種頭比較大，\N一般呈內凹或斜面，以此來撞擊水面激起水花的路亞。\N波扒的頭輕腳重，在水中靜止時，呈頭上腳下傾斜狀漂浮。\N個人覺得這個波扒的翻譯挺形象的。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 你曬得好黑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我從早到晚都在船上跑來跑去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春倒是沒怎麼曬黑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也曬黑了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為小春老是偷懶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪好狡猾 就會自己裝乖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:02:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎樣 有意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有話要跟你講
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這周內應該就可以出院哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 要慶祝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用特地麻煩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}錢貓杯 金槍魚 內有高價沙丁魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 值得慶賀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪和我要給凱特慶祝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.17,0:03:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要送她什麼禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 還是送條魚比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓奶奶吃到我親手釣上來的魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:26.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要釣什麼魚 我幫你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚哇 真不錯哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶也很喜歡金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想釣一次看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣金槍魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.07,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一群悠閒的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(抵達江之島)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山日日 報告書我讀了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是很奇怪的事件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問了一下當地的員警
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次那些衝浪的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看也不像是… 在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個事件 我這邊也已經得到情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 這次的狀況和飛機船舶的情況有點不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意到的時候時間已經過了 地點也轉移了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與百慕大綜合症應該有點關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山日日 我命令你調查的應該不是這件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這我明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續你的任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DUCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DUCK！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之島…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神隱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神隱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事情問我爺爺比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的爺爺 是這裡的宮司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}宮司：神社的最高神官，神社的專職神職人員，男的叫宮司，女的叫巫女。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是鎮長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:01.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 繪裡香你完全變了個樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 適合我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還輪不到阿基拉你說我怪嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就是我爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺 阿基拉說想問你有關神隱的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基拉 要小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要點就是不能老是吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔皮歐卡 拜拜~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是這個島自古以來流傳下來的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製造神隱的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有平息神隱的仙女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍和仙女？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得很荒唐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問這個龍 是暗喻某樣事物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍就是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 龍不是虛構的動物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神隱也真實存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只是碰巧處於平和時期而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最近總是有些隱隱不安的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望是錯覺而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜歡長鬍子的魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice吐槽！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好討厭冷笑話 真心討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鯰魚是也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要釣金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚頂器腰帶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}由於船釣時，水深流快，以及海魚咬鉤猛，\N掙扎力強，船釣時與魚僵持時用於固定釣竿和保護腰部的一種專門的腰帶。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用這個支撐住釣竿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為金槍魚體型很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有這個的話 整個釣竿都會被帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擬餌就用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,pencil bait（鉛筆型路亞）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}pencil_bait（鉛筆型路亞）:這一款路亞十分容易與其他類型的路亞區分開來，\N最大的識別點是這款路亞沒有整流板，而且大多是長條型，\N身體柱型而長或身長面尾部幼型狀就像一枝鉛筆一樣，故而得名。\N整流板就是有些路亞嘴裡突出的那塊唇片，用來壓水用的。\N像最開始他們用來練習的minnow的整流板就很大。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,pencil 鉛筆～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 因為像鉛筆一樣形狀很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以單卷線時不會有動作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣 壓低釣竿 讓擬餌潛入海底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝成誘餌 讓它稍微遊動之後 扯至海面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是用jerking的誘餌技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣重複 讓金槍魚上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順利的話 在它浮到海面的時候金槍魚會來咬鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小島 蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣金槍魚最重要的是 正確的拋鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚的警戒心很強 不能隨便地靠近它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放過每一次機會 所以必須得正確地拋鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BINGO！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意的不只這點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要釣大魚最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是垂釣者和控船者的團隊協作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團隊協作~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算上鉤了 金槍魚逃的很快且掙扎力很強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以控船的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很有難度啊 釣金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 一定會釣上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是地點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然拋鉤和團隊協作是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不找到它們的所在地的話 一切都是空話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向下壓杆 讓擬餌下潛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝成誘餌 讓它稍微遊動之後 扯至海面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花 櫻花會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻 嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 那裡有好多水鳥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不往那邊去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明海？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明是明亮的明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}明海是江之島海面上的人工魚礁，據說有很多魚群聚集在此。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是人造魚礁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}魚礁：由海底隆起而形成的淺海岩堆，為魚群易於聚集的地方。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚礁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了魚類的繁殖和生存 人為的在水裡設置的障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒聽懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單來說就是讓魚大量地聚在一起的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 那裡不能去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那裡禁止釣魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明有魚 為什麼要禁止呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只屬於當地人的秘密場所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實並沒有規定說禁止釣魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是當地的傢伙真的都不會去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再談論這種沒營養的話題了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以前那附近好像有漁船消失過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小傢伙們 這一個月辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都變成硬錚錚的男兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也幫了我大忙呢 謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才是承蒙您關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長 3Q~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年的慣例
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情的確是有那麼些雀躍…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不這麼做的話就沒個完的 準備上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:37.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不錯 變得自然多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂船長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在背後默默協助釣者的硬漢之活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認真地傾聽釣魚者的聲音 用心地注意他們的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把船開往他們最容易釣上魚的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的接近魚群
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也會搶在金槍魚的前進方向處等待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬鉤後就立刻縮短距離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.86,0:11:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.53,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船上的事什麼都可以問哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明海裡也有金槍魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近誰也沒有去過那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為有船隻莫名消失了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼嘛你 是你說想要我教你船隻的操縱方法我才教你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我只是有點在意而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 差不多要回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 離日落還有一段時間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解你們還想釣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是潮界線已經發生了改變 而且我等會還有個聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}潮界：兩條潮流在海面上相遇時形成的帶狀線，見於寒流和暖流相匯等處。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們可以拜託別人出海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不准去明海哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可以去 聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋啊 到處都沒有空船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣金槍魚不出海的話完全是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的話 坐我的船出海吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小島 蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 也讓我釣一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦 這是調查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋竿拋了很多次啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為位置不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我確實有聽說過有人在這附近釣到過金槍魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 船長他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是那裡絕對有金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話就不得不去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很想釣到吧 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要釣到 一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次見到啊 這絕贊的釣魚聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基拉 慢慢地靠近魚群
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我一定會釣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要自己釣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好距離哦 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要讓它逃了哦 機會只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼 給我好好看清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要慌 回想練習往鐵桶裡拋的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之島蓋飯哦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,江之 小島 蓋飯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼做來著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 jerking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 向下壓杆 讓擬餌下潛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝成魚餌 讓它遊動一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯至海面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 你要逃到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等它停下來 不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,線不會到頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會的 保持這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在 收線！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,縮短距離 阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 停船了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超 超級可惜的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不甘心呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪是不行的 讓我來釣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 還有一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管釣多少次都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 要相信他啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是小雪釣的就沒有意義了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 奶奶在等著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.34,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻 我想夏樹就快回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小櫻 乖乖等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託冷靜點 阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也回答我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能聽到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也給我冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚停止掙扎了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好機會！收線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定給我卷上來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠近點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.96,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.31,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,釣上來了呢 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人費心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱特也很會高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝我做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己釣上來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多虧了大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個魚不動了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明海消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明海不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是在哪兒釣魚忘了時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 平八先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一條都沒釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天海神大人好像心情不大好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是那些追著魚群跑到明海那邊去的褻瀆者的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現明海了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候跑到那麼遠去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間移動？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料減少了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這比較像是記憶缺失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是記憶操縱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前所未見的巨大金槍魚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.77,0:17:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能有那種金槍魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,百年不見了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.23,0:17:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對不住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 進船艙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚人 外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你終於露出真面目了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類可真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 是小步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在這片的港口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湘南港那邊的人也說沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}yacht_harbor：是遊艇港，\N江之島的遊艇港就是湘南港，這種港口主要是休閒用船。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫忙找下明海附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.67,0:18:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是青春丸號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:40.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表情真嚇人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淋點水笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 江之島
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是跟你說了很危險的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你們都還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船長～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我提議要去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是我想釣金槍魚才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是一群大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏樹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你們知道給人家添了多少麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我有…多擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了啊 小保
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揪心～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶出院了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我才第一次感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏天即將完結多麼讓人感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件衣服真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 JATI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JATI
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}JATI:這個詞我實在不知道要把它劃分到哪個語種，\N印度語裡ms有神聖的意思，馬來語裡jati_diri是什麼一致，同一的意思，也就是和諧？\N說到底我 也不確定是否是JATI還是GRAZIE（義大利語謝謝）。各位可自行腦補。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時開始有一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能看到小春真正的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道其原因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是更久之後的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,義三他們那邊還在釣魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.11,0:21:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在跳江之島舞
